{"source_id":"W739","raw_fingerprint":"https://nintendoeverything.com/farming-simulator-gains-modhub-on-nintendo-switch-2-over-4000-mods-available/","timestamp":"2026-05-12T17:10:34Z","url":"https://nintendoeverything.com/farming-simulator-gains-modhub-on-nintendo-switch-2-over-4000-mods-available/","author":"Nintendo Everything","genre":"games","subcategory_id":"A9","category_name":"他機種移植","importance":"B","summary":"Nintendo Switch版『ファーミングシミュレーター』にModHubが追加され、4,000以上のユーザー作成MODが利用可能になりました。これはNintendoコンソール初のModHub機能です。","title_tags":["ファーミングシミュレーター","Nintendo Switch","ModHub","MOD"],"entity_tags":["Nintendo","Farming Simulator"],"flags":{"source_role":"公式","speed":"速報","spoiler":"なし","language":"ja","content_type":"text","source_reliability":"公式確定","cross_genre":"ゲーム単独"},"dedup_key":"farming_simulator_modhub_nintendo_switch_release","raw_text":"Farming Simulator gains ModHub on Nintendo Switch 2, over 4,000 mods available\n<p>Starting today, Farming Simulator: Signature Edition players on Nintendo Switch 2 can access the game&#8217;s ModHub. This is the first time the feature has been available on Nintendo&#8217;s console. ModHub lets players enjoy mods to extend and customize their virtual farms. Over 4,000 modifications are available to download directly in-game. These feature more maps, machines, and gameplay that are user-generated.","risk_level":"low","streamer_influence_score":0,"clip_virality_score":0,"game_trend_from_streamers_score":0,"live_trend_score":0,"video_trend_score":0,"freshness_score":100,"final_priority":"B","streamer_name":"","streamer_group":"","is_clip":false,"related_game_title":"","related_anime_title":""}
