{"source_id":"W703","raw_fingerprint":"https://automaton-media.com/articles/special-column/20260513-442714/","timestamp":"2026-05-13T03:00:01Z","url":"https://automaton-media.com/articles/special-column/20260513-442714/","author":"Automaton (RSS)","genre":"games","subcategory_id":"A11","category_name":"DLC","importance":"B","summary":"基本プレイ無料オープンワールド『NTE』に新キャラ「潯（ほとり）」が登場。5月13日より利用可能で、時間停止能力を駆使したユニークなゲームプレイが楽しめる。","title_tags":["NTE","Neverness to Everness","新キャラ","潯","ほとり","時間停止"],"entity_tags":["NTE","Neverness to Everness","潯","ほとり"],"flags":{"source_role":"公式","speed":"速報","spoiler":"なし","language":"ja","content_type":"text","source_reliability":"公式確定","cross_genre":"ゲーム単独"},"dedup_key":"nte_neverness_to_everness_new_character_hotori_time_stop_available_may_13","raw_text":"基本プレイ無料「街」オープンワールド『NTE』新キャラ「潯（ほとり）」は“時間停止”を街歩きでも使えて、チートみたいに遊び放題。強いというかズルい、酒好きテキトーお姉さん\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://automaton-media.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/20260513-442714-header.jpg\" width=\"1600\" /></p>『NTE: Neverness to Everness』にて5月13日より登場する新プレイアブルキャラクター「潯（ほとり）」について紹介していく。","risk_level":"low","streamer_influence_score":0,"clip_virality_score":0,"game_trend_from_streamers_score":0,"live_trend_score":0,"video_trend_score":0,"freshness_score":100,"final_priority":"B","streamer_name":"","streamer_group":"","is_clip":false,"related_game_title":"","related_anime_title":""}
