{"source_id":"W739","raw_fingerprint":"https://nintendoeverything.com/arrest-made-after-man-threatens-to-blow-up-nintendos-headquarters/","timestamp":"2026-05-13T02:43:27Z","url":"https://nintendoeverything.com/arrest-made-after-man-threatens-to-blow-up-nintendos-headquarters/","author":"Nintendo Everything","genre":"games","subcategory_id":"F4","category_name":"人事","importance":"S","summary":"任天堂本社への爆破予告で27歳無職の男が逮捕された。京都府警が5月12日に逮捕し、威力業務妨害の疑いが持たれている。男は任天堂に送付した封筒に「皆殺しにしてやる」「俺の計画は…」などのメッセージを入れていた。","title_tags":["任天堂","逮捕","爆破予告"],"entity_tags":["任天堂","京都府警"],"flags":{"source_role":"公式","speed":"速報","spoiler":"なし","language":"ja","content_type":"text","source_reliability":"公式確定","cross_genre":"ゲーム単独"},"dedup_key":"arrest_made_after_man_threatens_to_blow_up_nintendos_headquarters","raw_text":"Arrest made after man threatens to blow up Nintendo’s headquarters\n<p>Reports are emerging from Japan that a 27-year-old unemployed man has been arrested for threating to blow up Nintendo&#8217;s headquarters. Kyoto police made the arrest today, May 12. The man was arrested on grounds of suspected obstruction of business. In envelopes sent to Nintendo, the man included messages such as &#8220;I’m going to blow you all up&#8221; and &#8220;My plans...</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://nintendoever","risk_level":"high","streamer_influence_score":0,"clip_virality_score":0,"game_trend_from_streamers_score":0,"live_trend_score":0,"video_trend_score":0,"freshness_score":100,"final_priority":"A","streamer_name":"","streamer_group":"","is_clip":false,"related_game_title":"","related_anime_title":""}
